{
  "stem": "26576.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People's army was the Russian-- AK, the were very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I had a few times that I had to travel when it was a holiday or something, I would go back home to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had a few times, the people were taken off the train and shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, so-- You constantly had it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You had the Germans or you had the Russian and then-- then you had the Poles that were very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Although, in Lodz, we had a lot of Poles at the university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But this was a different crowd, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were people that were mostly-- either they were pro-Jewish or pro-communist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were fighting among themselves, so always the Jew was the scapegoat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was studying medicine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband's name is Abram Zeleznikov.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my first impression, when I first met at that youth camp, we were all laughing, because he was really-- they called him the partisan.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If one remembers that this was 1946, and the war finished, he came out of the partisans in 1945.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was only a year from that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- he was very-- he was a very moody man, which he stayed on up to now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, he could be in a wonderful mood and then he would go very angry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was full of anger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was very young, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think he was 20 at that stage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, he was born-- he was 21.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- but we're only friends at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I did not-- nothing was further from my mind than marriage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wanted to study.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I wanted to stay on in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But things did change bit by bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
